Sorter mode:
0 match all filters
1 match any
2 match none

match item : export 2 

1)Concatenate an instruction:
OP Code Instruction [8 bits] / [PARAMETER1] / [POTENTIAL PARAMETER2]
ex:
define steel HASH("ITEMSTEELINGOT")
ins r0 steel 8 32                      #insert 32 bits hash in 8th place (after OP code) in r0
ins r0 SorterInstruction.SorterInstruction.FilterPrefabHashEquals 0 8   #insert 8bits opcode  in 0th position in r0

2) insert rule in sorter, ex:
put sorter 0 r0 #insert rule r0 in stack0


EXEMPLE

alias sorter d0
define Hash1 HASH("ItemSteelIngot")
s sorter Mode 1 # Any
clr sorter # erase any stale instructions in RAM

ins r0 steel 8 32 
or r0 r0 SorterInstruction.FilterPrefabHashEquals
put sorter 0 r0


LIST OF INSTRUCTIONS 

Sort by Hash equal:
define Hash1 HASH("ItemSteelIngot")
ins r0 SorterInstruction.FilterPrefabHashEquals 0 8
ins r0 Hash1 8 32

Sort by Hash NOT equal:
define Hash1 HASH("ItemSteelIngot")
ins r0 SorterInstruction.FilterPrefabHashNotEqual 0 8
ins r0 Hash1 8 32

Sort by sorting class equal:
define SortingClass 3
ins r0 SorterInstruction.FilterSortingClassCompare 0 8
#add r0 r0 256 add preshifted CONDOP
ins r0 SortingClass 16 32

Sort by sorting item type:
define SortingType 3
ins r0 SorterInstruction.FilterSlotTypeCompare 0 8
#add r0 r0 256 add preshifted CONDOP
ins r0 SortingType 16 32

Sort by filter quantity (vs stack size of the items in the import slot)
define Quantity 50
ins r0 SorterInstruction.FilterQuantityCompare 0 8
#add r0 r0 256 add preshifted CONDOP
ins r0 Quantity 16 32

Limit amount of execution (Ensures the next executable instruction will only return true a specified number of times. Each time it returns true, it decrements by one.)
define Iterations 10
ins r0 SorterInstruction.LimitNextExecutionByCount 0 8
ins r0 Iteration 8 40


Conditional Operation (CONDOP)	Value	Pre-shifted (ready to add)
Equals	                        0	    0
Greater	                        1	    256 (ex: add r0 r0 256)
Less	                          2	    512
NotEquals	                      3	    768

FilterSlotTypeCompare 
None	0		Helmet	1		Suit	2 Back	3		GasFilter	4		GasCanister	5	 Motherboard	6		Circuitboard	7		DataDisk	8	Organ	9		Ore	10	(Includes reagent mixes from recycler and ices)	Plant	11	
