Sorting classes
0	Default	Items without a specific category assigned.
1	Kits	All construction kits (e.g., Kit (Battery), Kit (Wall)).
2	Tools	Handheld tools like Drills, Wrenches, and Arc Welders.
3	Resources	Refined materials like Copper Ingots or Steel Plates.
4	Food / Seeds	All consumable food items and planting seeds.
5	Clothing	Uniforms, space suits, helmets, and backpacks.
6	Appliances	Small machines such as Arc Furnaces or Microwave ovens.
7	Atmospherics	Pipe components, tanks, gas filters, and valves.
8	Storage	Containers like Crates, Lockers, and Canisters.
9	Ores	All raw, unrefined mineral rocks.
10	Ices	Raw frozen rocks: Volatile, Oxite, and Water Ice.
